properties.Name: GeographicArea
properties.Description:
A geographic area is a geographic formation, area or body that is bounded by location points and has an area.

The geographic area is defined by a series of ordered vertices that form the corners of the polygon.

Columns.Name: GeographicAreaId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Geographic Area.

Columns.Name: GeographicAreaName
Columns.Description: The name of a Geographic Area.

Columns.Name: GeographicAreaDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Geographic Area.

Columns.Name: GeographicAreaTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Geographic Area Type.

Columns.Name: GeographicAreaUnits
Columns.Description: The size of the geographic area expressed in UOM.

Columns.Name: GeographicAreaUomId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Unit Of Measure.

Columns.Name: GeographicAreaGeojsonRepresentation
Columns.Description: A pointer to a GeoJSON representation of a geographic area.
